videos.description: Alex James takes it 24 yards to the end zone for the Chanticleers first touchdown.
videos.headline: Coastal Carolina's  James evades the defense for the TD

videos.description: Sean McGuire connects with Brandon Gaston to take the lead in the second quarter.
videos.headline: Western Illinois' McGuire finds Gaston for the 19-yard score

videos.description: Max Norris takes it in from one-yard out to extend the Leathernecks lead in the first half.
videos.headline: Western Illinois' Norris pounds it in for TD

videos.description: Sean McGuire connects with his tight-end as the Leathernecks pile it on against Coastal Carolina.
videos.headline: McGuire to Conrady to extend lead

videos.description: Devon Sanders sprints through the middle of the Coastal Carolina defense for the 80-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Sanders takes it 80 yards untouched for a TD
